metadata.name: Palm Tree Hands / Uncharted Emotion
metadata.description:
Behind the one you see at first glance, hides another. And I wonder if you see it too! When rotated to the left it looks like a person crunching and embracing themselves which significantly shifts the artwork meaning as opposed to its standard position.

The fact that the double meaning was at first unplanned, made me pick the second name "Uncharted Emotion" and put it next to its original "Palm Tree Hands".
